  "title": "No See, No Tick",
  "description": "Configurable performance mod that increases entity performance by stopping ticks based on distance",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\"No See, No Tick\" is continuation of \"It Shall Not Tick\" by Gaz_ (MIT Licensed) which was abandoned</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">An alternative to \"Does It Tick?\" by TeamDeusVult for newer Minecraft versions.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Allows up to 4x performance increase in large modpacks by disabling entities' ticking that are too far away from the player, with a configurable distance and blacklist.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod uses the same configuration template as the \"It Shall Not Tick\" mod.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1070190643466473493/1081099736825724978/Rdcwxax.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"454\" height=\"323\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">(Image credits from <a class=\"anchor-1X4H4q anchorUnderlineOnHover-wiZFZ_\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/does-it-tick\" role=\"button\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/does-it-tick\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/does-it-tick</a>)&nbsp;</span></p>",
